When was the last time you called your mother and said that you loved her?
附加记录：    

I wrote this SCP to explore the relationship between a mother who prioritizes work over family, and her grief in doing so. This is the second SCP from Grant's Zoo for Cybernetically Enhanced Bears, previously seen in SCP-2579.

Thank you to FloppyPhoenix for crit.

